{"tid":1641400,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"就臨時禁制令之申請作法等事宜嘅簡單社評","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:33:25.000Z","uid":320849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa998a4fdbe401f3eacb74db5f5fb2e9845b28f","tid":1641400,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:24:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">請注意：正片使用粉紅色字體</div><br />\n相信大家都瞭解，呢排泛民派申請司法覆核同臨時禁制令，所以背景資料就唔多講啦。對於呢件事，我嘅疑問只有一點：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">泛民派想搞邊科？？？玩政治騷？？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">本人自己就讀於法律相關學科</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">（具體學科唔講太多，以免被人起底）</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">，連我呢啲 Green law student 都知道嘅嘢，擁有大量法律從業人員嘅泛民派冇可能唔知&mdash;&mdash;如果冇確鑿且強而有力嘅證據顯示相關議題違反憲制性法律同BORO嘅話，高等法院係「唔會」批出臨時禁制令嘅。<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講「佢地時間匆忙，冇時間想太多嘢」。我自己都可以通過對於&quot;<em>To confer on the Chief Executive in Council power to make regulations on <strong>occasions of emergency or public danger</strong>.</em>&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">（簡稱&quot;<em>Emergency Regulations Ordinance</em>&quot;，中文好似叫《緊急狀態條例》；因為要講述立法原意而引用長標題，不便之處，敬請原諒。）</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">嘅立法原意等相關概念，係當時就知道如何來反駁相關程序與&quot;<em>Prohibition of Face Masking</em>&quot; Regulation</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">（俗稱《禁蒙面法》；其實佢只不過係「附屬常規」，唔係「獨立法例」or「附屬法例」，「法」係錯誤叫法，不過重點唔係呢度）</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">嘅引用立例作法。試問如果「並沒有意味著香港進入緊急狀態」</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">（林鄭自己講嘅嘢）</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">嘅情況下，點樣可以引用一個建基於且用來應對「<strong>緊急狀態</strong>」嘅《<strong>緊急狀態</strong>條例》？如果今次放過佢，係唔係以後都係日常生活都可以引用呢條條例來搞搞震？！咁係唔係違憲？<br />\n<br />\n呢啲證據比比皆是，你是但寫幾條係狀書入邊都得啦；何況佢哋泛民又唔係得一個律師，而且我呢啲 Green law student 都想到嘅嘢，一定會有泛民律師想到，點可以就咁寫啲泛泛而談嘅垃圾嘢俾高院申請禁制令？</span><br />\n<br />\n我越想越唔明，點解？點解佢哋泛民要咁樣寫篇垃圾交俾高院開庭？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">事情已經發生咗，我覺得好無奈，漸漸開始懷疑當初我揀咗讀law，究竟係唔係真係reach到我當初所相信嘅Rule of Law。嗨⋯⋯香港人加油。</span>"},{"pid":"44156c2ca70cf7b12feea3a650af5d35cf8e97ba","tid":1641400,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a3117999eaf7b97eaf2e27bb3057c6594be984","tid":1641400,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"pish I"},{"pid":"a266d85f7e2199f247db1e21d42e9df860eb8ba4","tid":1641400,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"美國國會疑似有全港警察名單<br />\n<br />\n謝sir應該已向美國篤灰 (含分析)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c9a1723e039d1122bc8299a9ec4c7bf745cb2e8","tid":1641400,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:31:38.000Z","msg":"pish II"},{"pid":"485f6e65acc865e035cf4a50542ad29222bb3691","tid":1641400,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:31:48.000Z","msg":"pish III"},{"pid":"940edbd97231ad4eaf5c61e59721fdfbcfd9989a","tid":1641400,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"pish IV"},{"pid":"189f3f8a4758affa2b0414278b0d0db2f1a1d1f0","tid":1641400,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"pish V"},{"pid":"2fe5d44f112e8d2d0f897f26c7b4f4a8f5d6c9d9","tid":1641400,"uid":320849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:33:25.000Z","msg":"順便一提，今晚新港城見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}